*Sedim* u parku i čitam knjigu (I'm sitting in the park and reading a book).
*Sedela* je u kući i gledala televiziju (She was sitting in the house and watching television).
*Sednimo* u automobil i krenimo (Let's get in the car and go).
*Sedeo* je u hodniku tri sata (He was sitting in the hallway for three hours).
*Sedeli* su na terasi i razgovarali (They were sitting on the terrace and talking).